&lt;li&gt;Create media plans matching partner goals and provide ad product offerings to partners&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide weekly reports to advertisers with sound optimizations to improve campaign performance and achieve advertisers’ KPI&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
