&lt;li&gt;Present compelling category and advertiser specific business trends and insights&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively pitch cross-sell and upsell opportunities to advertisers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a partner advocate during pilots and internal cross functional feedback sessions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compile campaign wrap reports owing follow up and actionable takeaways&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with cross functional teams and spearhead the creation of the Quarterly Business Review; present campaign insights to CPG advertisers with an analytical mindset&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a deep understanding of Instacart’s evolving full funnel advertising suite and strategy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively participates in gap to goal planning and manages quota over multiple business units&amp;nbsp;&lt;

